[normal] 
[normal]Would you even consider resigning in view of the fact that these people got through your net?
[normal]David Lawton[bold]: At this point in relation to the SFO questions, that is still a matter that is under investigation at this stage.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q140 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Mr Binley:[bold] Letting them on to the List is not a matter that is still under investigation.
