[normal]David Lawton[bold]: It is not something the FCA has given a huge amount of thought to.
[normal] 
[normal]Obviously, for 
[normal]UK
[normal] companies already, under the Companies Act, there is a requirement to have a shareholders’ register available.
[normal] 
