[normal]David Lawton[bold]: When that legislation takes effect, we will be working with the Government to embed it in the 
[normal]UK
[normal] rules.
[normal] 
[normal]Typically, European legislation is implemented through a combination of changes to law and complementary changes to the FCA rules.
