[normal]David Lawton[bold]: I am not responsible for setting the name.
[normal]Chair:[bold] I quite appreciate that, but I would welcome your opinion.
[normal]David Lawton[bold]: The important point I would want to leave the Committee with is that we are a capital markets regulator.
[normal] 
[normal]We are not a 
[normal]companies
[normal] regulator.
[normal] 
[normal]There are a number of things that are of concern to you about company behaviour, which have some bearing on our capital markets regulatory objectives, and we have talked particularly about financial crime.
[normal] 
[normal]There are a number of other things that have no bearing on it directly, and it is important that the Committee is clear that we are not a 
[normal]companies
[normal] regulator.
[normal]Chair:[bold] I think I know the answer to the next question, but I am still going to ask Paul
[normal]&#xa0;
